data.description: This property has it all with room for the Chickens and Horses. Country living on 3 Acres just 20 min from Pueblo. Farmhouse Style Decor.  Main house 2 bedrooms 1 bath with wood burning stove compliments the HVAC system and Remodeled kitchen.  Additional living space in the detached guest house 1 bedroom 1 bath and Living rm with kitchenette.  Detached 3 car Garage with Workshop, Wood Burning Stove, Swamp cooler and car lift. Barn has 4 stalls, electricity and hay feeder.  Commercial grade 6 burner gas stove in kitchen,  All kitchen appliances included.  Fenced arena, coral.  Updated Electrical.  Property has dual water sources, city water and well water and fully paid solar system.   New roof on the Main and Guest House, and two RV hookups.
